LEGEND:                                                                         
  D OR DD  = Door                                                               
  @@       = Spinner                                                            
  **       = Darkness                                                           
  TT       = Trap                                                               
  < OR > OR /\ OR \/  = ONE WAY WALLS - ALLOWABLE DIRECTION WITH ARROW          
                                                                                
                                                                                
