  1 = stairs up                                                                 
  2 = message of some sort                                                      
  3 = silence (quiets bardsong)                                                 
  4 = hits decrease                                                             
  5 = explosion - one time hit decrease                                         
  6 = darkness                                                                  
  7 = darkness and hit decrease                                                 
  8 = in blood: chaos                                                           
  9 = hit increase                                                              
 10 = magic decrease                                                            
                                                                                
